* BAT85 — Schottky barrier diode (Vishay).
*
* 30V / 200 mA Schottky — small RF/UHF detector, fast switching,
* low Vf (~0.3V @ 1mA). SPICE — typical Schottky model (Duncan,
* Vishay datasheet).
*
* subcategory: schottky
* Pins:
*   A — anode, K — cathode.
.SUBCKT BAT85 A K
D1 A K D_BAT85
.MODEL D_BAT85 D(Is=300n N=1.04 Rs=2.0 Cjo=10p M=0.5 Bv=30 Ibv=10u Tt=0 Eg=0.69 Xti=2)
.ENDS BAT85
